take some selfies
and get really weird?

12:49.792 --> 12:51.708
Why do you keep
coming to her stuff
and supporting her, then,

12:51.708 --> 12:53.875
if you think
she's so manipulative?

12:53.875 --> 12:56.834
Uh, because I will always
be in love with her.

12:56.834 --> 12:59.000
Okay, fuck this.
We live together.

12:59.000 --> 13:01.458
Enjoy it while it lasts
'cause I'm gonna get her back,
motherfucker.

13:01.458 --> 13:02.792
No, this is
fucking bullshit.

13:02.792 --> 13:04.291
You think she really
likes you, monkey face?

13:04.291 --> 13:05.291
You're just
a chess move, buddy.

13:05.291 --> 13:07.083
You motherfucker.
Just pull over!

13:07.083 --> 13:09.500
All right, buddy.
Hey. Chill.

13:09.500 --> 13:12.083
I would never, ever
call you a mother effer
for serious.

13:12.083 --> 13:14.125
It's not my game.
You know what I mean?

13:14.125 --> 13:17.041
It's not my jam,
it's not who I am.

13:17.041 --> 13:19.417
I know where you are
right now.

13:19.417 --> 13:22.250
Adrift in the river
of Mimi-Rose.

13:25.542 --> 13:28.708
I get the feeling
that you didn't really
like my show.

13:28.708 --> 13:32.208
Well, that's crazy
'cause I fuckin' loved
your show.

13:32.208 --> 13:33.959
You know you can
be honest with me.

13:33.959 --> 13:36.583
I find criticism
to be super valuable.

13:36.583 --> 13:41.333
