when I have absolutely
nothing to criticize.

13:41.333 --> 13:44.875
I mean, the show was perfect.
It was Beyoncé to me.

13:44.875 --> 13:46.959
Okay.

13:46.959 --> 13:49.417
Glad you found it
to be affecting.

13:49.417 --> 13:51.375
I did.
