13:51.375 --> 13:54.875
I didn't really have
as much time to work on it
as I would've liked

13:54.875 --> 13:57.583
'cause I got sucked into
writing this stupid book.

13:57.583 --> 14:01.250
- You're, uh,
writing a book?
- I'm trying.

14:01.250 --> 14:02.959
It's a psychosexual
thriller

14:02.959 --> 14:05.000
told from the perspective
of a dead woman

14:05.000 --> 14:06.083
who solves
her own murder

14:06.083 --> 14:09.250
using hologram technology
that she invented.

14:09.250 --> 14:14.083
I think it'll probably suck,
but I just always try to work
outside my comfort zone

14:14.083 --> 14:15.250
'cause that's
the only way you grow,

14:15.250 --> 14:17.542
but I'm not
a real writer like you.

14:17.542 --> 14:19.625
I'm not a writer at all.
I mean, not anymore.

14:19.625 --> 14:21.250
That's not
what Adam says.

14:21.250 --> 14:23.500
I quit, and I've literally
never been happier.

14:23.500 --> 14:25.750
Your finger's
touching my shoulder.

14:27.583 --> 14:29.250
Hey, um, could we make
the turn up here?

14:29.250 --> 14:31.250
That would be great.
We need to try
a different route.

14:31.250 --> 14:33.917
